sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Retrieves a list of firewalls available to the specified project.

Inputs:

  • Project ID - Unique ID of the project.

Outputs:

  • Firewalls - JSON object containing Labels and Names of the firewalls.

Error Messages:

  • Invalid Project ID.
  • Invalid authorization header. The access token you're using is either expired or invalid.

To use this action, a corresponding Google Cloud Virtual Network connection and credential must be created and associated with the Google Cloud Virtual Network Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.

Retrieves a list of firewalls available to the specified project.

Inputs:

  • Project ID - Unique ID of the project.

Outputs:

  • Firewalls - JSON object containing Labels and Names of the firewalls.

Error Messages:

  • Invalid Project ID.
  • Invalid authorization header. The access token you're using is either expired or invalid.

To use this action, a corresponding Google Cloud Virtual Network connection and credential must be created and associated with the Google Cloud Virtual Network Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.
